{"tid":418055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【用鉛筆+量角器擊敗美軍】北韓以前製作既反美卡通","createTime":"2017-09-29T08:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T02:35:06.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ffb23380a612ea177a19677b3cb01f9ff54a96","tid":418055,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpCsoQcS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpCsoQcS.jpg&h=c73ae2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">由北韓國營的朝鮮4工作室（SEK Studio）製作的長壽電視動畫「松鼠和刺蝟」。（圖片擷取自文中YouTube影片）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓近日與美國彼此的軍事示威引起全球關注，日前北韓官方媒體更釋出北韓導彈擊中美軍戰鬥機和航母的假照片，以及白宮遭轟炸的示意影片。<br />\n<br />\n除了假照片和影片，北韓也會製作動畫作為反美官方宣傳。據外電報導，在影片網站YouTube上可見北韓官方的宣傳動畫。北韓於金日成時期開始，便使用動畫當作反美宣傳，傳教育北韓的孩童。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>YouTube上一部約1960年代出品，以兒童為主角的北韓製動畫可見，一位小男孩在他的桌子上睡著後，夢見自己正在與美軍戰鬥。而後，這位小男孩用鉛筆和量角器製作出火箭發射器，並用這些「鉛筆火箭」擊沉入侵的美軍漂浮坦克。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n金正日政府也繼承此一手法製作官方宣傳動畫，向北韓孩童傳達反美訊息。例如，由北韓國營的朝鮮4工作室（SEK Studio）製作的長壽電視動畫「松鼠和刺蝟」。「松鼠和刺蝟」的故事主題，是一群居住在名為「花嶺」地區的動物們，必須向代表日本的黃鼠狼和代表美國的狼作戰。據報導，一位北韓導遊說「這部動畫在北韓很經典，大家都知道松鼠與刺蝟」。<br />\n<br />\n看了這些YouTube上的宣傳動畫，網友表示：「北韓政府有錢做宣傳動畫給小孩看，卻沒錢餵飽他們的人民？」、「金正恩小時候該不會是看這些動畫長大吧？」，也有網友認為「這些動畫的品質很不錯」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ujtp-70zQME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dujtp-70zQME&d=lbtpjeH8lVj6cnSWx67hK%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=44e760b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ujtp-70zQME</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HuXJBJWR36Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHuXJBJWR36Y&d=lbtpjeH8lVj6cnSWx67hK%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=e46bddf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HuXJBJWR36Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2208246\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2208246&d=lbtpjeH8lVj6cnSWx67hK%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=8f2c2f99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2208246&h=0ab40c97\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2208246</a>"},{"pid":"ea442fa84d1bc603ce8c20135a8bc5a3ebc84e31","tid":418055,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T22:10:35.000Z","msg":"仲好過支那個乜羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa67fec88d79a1d4e972582f11f7d6f2f805f34b","tid":418055,"uid":80294,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T22:21:16.000Z","msg":"睇嚟 北韓 唔少人都睇得起 電視 亦都有渠道接觸到西方資訊<br />\n搞到要政府 揼本 整返啲質素唔係太差嘅卡通片 嚟洗腦"},{"pid":"122cf7e275f5279a1a34d1c9120c4cd011f92402","tid":418055,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T23:16:48.000Z","msg":"有design<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9625f91f60c016c11199fbf1fb886eab6f3e91e7","tid":418055,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T23:40:06.000Z","msg":"真係60年代咁高水準？"},{"pid":"96d72c412b6de3b51ff822eb96069f225f455508","tid":418055,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係60年代咁高水準？</blockquote><br />\n北韓當年發達過中韓，與日本同級架！"},{"pid":"d4d28d93b1f5bd6c64e4c11e06bbc8cb009241aa","tid":418055,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇嚟 北韓 唔少人都睇得起 電視 亦都有渠道接觸到西方資訊<br />\n搞到要政府 揼本 整返啲質素唔係太差嘅卡通片 嚟洗腦</blockquote><br />\n北韓係家家戶戶都一定要裝電視<br />\n部電視仲唔閂得 只可以較細聲啲"},{"pid":"379a40e4f348f17dec9ac5741b3a775429ee6a4c","tid":418055,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:28:27.000Z","msg":"有3d<img src=